      <item>
        <title>@frontity-codenawis theme</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[mymakarim]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p><strong>Frontity-Codenawis theme</strong> is built with <img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/heart.png?v=9" title=":heart:" class="emoji" alt=":heart:"> on top of mars-theme with lots of more features added into it <img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/sunglasses.png?v=9" title=":sunglasses:" class="emoji" alt=":sunglasses:"></p>
<ol>
<li>Sharing Buttons</li>
<li>Category based Posts in Homepage</li>
<li>Comment Section in Single Post Page</li>
<li>Grid System</li>
<li>Search</li>
<li>Categories in Navbar</li>
<li>Tags in post page</li>
<li>Better Pagination</li>
<li>Footer</li>
</ol>
<p>Let me know if you like it and if I should publish it as an npm package.<br>
Find me as <a class="mention" href="https://community.frontity.org/u/mymakarim">@mymakarim</a> or <span class="mention">@codenawis</span> on social media</p>
<p><img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/zap.png?v=9" title=":zap:" class="emoji" alt=":zap:"> Live demo<br>
<a href="http://newschin.mymakarim.vercel.app/" class="onebox" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">http://newschin.mymakarim.vercel.app/</a><br>
Source code available in Github. make sure to follow &amp; give me a <img src="https://community.frontity.org/images/emoji/apple/star.png?v=9" title=":star:" class="emoji" alt=":star:"><br>
